Science and technology related expenses
>This report refers to Japan's "science and technology-related expenditures" as the science and technology budget. Science and technology-related expenditure refers to the sum of (1) science and technology promotion expenses (expenses in the general account budget whose main purpose of expenditure is the promotion of science and technology), (2) other research-related expenses in the general account, and (3) science and technology-related expenses in the special account.

